septemspinosum
), Russia (
nigripes
), Ukraine : Polish Ukraine (
nigriceps
), Japan : Kanagawa : Yokohama (
japonicum
), Switzerland : Ticino [as Tessin ] ( flavoguttatum ), Russia : Primorsky Territory: Okeanskaja [on the coast near Vladivostok] (
dinurum
).
